{"tid":2506193,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德下任總理大熱倡強硬對華","createTime":"2021-04-27T06:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T13:31:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d8dae5172353d8002080615f26d936e8e1d52881","tid":2506193,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:59:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210427/FNJLLR42RNFGPAGRBQWZ73OZ7A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210427%2FFNJLLR42RNFGPAGRBQWZ73OZ7A%2F&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=fe0b76e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210427%2FFNJLLR42RNFGPAGRBQWZ73OZ7A%2F&h=72e281ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210427/FNJLLR42RNFGPAGRBQWZ73OZ7A/</a><br />\n<br />\n德下任總理大熱倡強硬對華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KWnTK0vDzas31PECoNT6hSUlINQ=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ER5PMAZMCFA2TMGN5GJRVQNDZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKWnTK0vDzas31PECoNT6hSUlINQ%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FER5PMAZMCFA2TMGN5GJRVQNDZY.jpg&h=92d9ba69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貝爾伯克<br />\n<br />\n下任德國總理大熱人選、綠黨黨魁貝爾伯克（Annalena Baerbock）表示，德國要以「對話且強硬」兼備的態度應對中國，以捍衞民主價值及人權。<br />\n<br />\n貝爾伯克接受《法蘭克福滙報》（Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung）的訪問於前日刊登。貝爾伯克指，歐洲應動用自身經濟力量，封殺中國以強迫勞動所生產的商品，並避免使用危及歐洲安全的通訊技術。她形容：「我們正處於兩種制度的角力：獨裁權力與自由民主。」<br />\n<br />\n她指出，中國在中亞及歐洲的基。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n轟俄威脅烏克蘭<br />\n<br />\n她亦將矛頭指向俄羅斯，斥對方近日在烏克蘭邊境增兵，並支持親俄武裝的行為。她支持烏克蘭申請加入北約（NATO）及歐盟，但認為「現階段最重要的是向俄國進一步施壓，令其履行明斯克協議」。該協議尋求和平結束烏克蘭東部衝突。她亦借機批評現屆德國政府，支持俄國「北溪2號」天然氣管道工程的決定。<br />\n<br />\n德國將於9月26日舉行國會選舉。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"e5aad826a9e1a56f2358cccd2a83c0366c917e07","tid":2506193,"uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:02:08.000Z","msg":"#Biden #歐盟 #德國<br />\n<br />\n黃世澤<br />\nBiden 訪歐能否重建歐盟反中政策 <br />\n黃世澤幾分鐘評論 <br />\n20210426<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6ymO9BA_2KY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6ymO9BA_2KY&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=595ff3eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6ymO9BA_2KY</a><br />\n<br />\nmartin oei<br />\n134K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n#Biden​ #歐盟​ #德國​<br />\n00:00​ Biden 訪歐能否重建歐盟反中政策<br />\n01:59​ 德國嘅政治轉變<br />\n11:41​ 法國嘅戴高樂主義思維<br />\n18:30​ 點解Biden拉攏亞美尼亞<br />\n<br />\n#綠黨​ #法國​ #中國​  #EU​ #評論​#StayHome​ #WithMe​ #跟我一樣​ #宅在家​<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2F&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=d11f37ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/</a>"},{"pid":"1356a69b887b0e5ed6dee3cd77226d8f1ee8509a","tid":2506193,"uid":77196,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:02:42.000Z","msg":"死肥婆終於收皮"},{"pid":"c4c9dd7d824d2eab84f7aa57133b9401243a4518","tid":2506193,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:03:23.000Z","msg":"Baerbock咁快變左大熱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nArmin Laschet<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008d1e97c5a6973c8059b2f0b35d8efafe2127a1","tid":2506193,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass